One Step Beyond was of course written by its wizards - but it incorporates
many ideas from other sources which simply were too good to be ignored.
We try to give credit wherever due, but don't jump on us if we forget
a thing or two.

Nightfall provided the basic mudlib (May 1997) to start off.
DEATH, conceived by Terry Pratchett, does do guest appearances since the dark
  times of LP mudding.
Intermud3 was invented by Deathblade, Rust, Beek, Descartes and Deathknight
  from the MudOS world. The actual demon is based on the code used in Lima.
